ing and were also identified as\nplanet candidates by human vetters. We also provide a homogeneously classified\nset of TESS candidates suitable for future training.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Apr 2019 18:04:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 May 2019 19:15:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
