 with superior electrical and mechanical\nproperties (revealed by tensile testing). The well distributed GNP\nnanoparticles acting as nanoheaters integrated in a thermosetting matrix, in\ncombination with excellent mechanical and electrical performances achieved for\nthe overall graphene/epoxy composites and the simplicity associated to the\nmethod, should open the door to novel industrial applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2019 09:04:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Apr 2019 14:50:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-10"}
